-- ══════════════════════════════════════
--  Rain Hub v5.0
-- ══════════════════════════════════════
--  v1.0 — Shoot Murd, Lock, Fake Speed,
--          Gun TP, Player ESP
--  v2.0 — Auto Farm (replaces Shoot Murd)
--          Noclip, tween to Coin_Server,
--          rainbow Highlight + part color,
--          0.5 transparency on coins,
--          DescendantRemoving ESP cleanup
--  v3.0 — Highlight parented to part for
--          true through-wall visibility,
--          Touched retargets next coin,
--          touchConn cleanup on despawn
--  v4.0 — Touch instantly retargets next
--          closest coin with no wait
--  v5.0 — Full slide-out MENU (Rain Hub
--          tab on left edge), pill toggles,
--          floating badge indicators appear
--          only when feature is ON,
--          PC + Mobile drag optimized,
--          coin ESP through-wall fixed
-- ══════════════════════════════════════
